11
00:07:10,699 --> 00:07:14,942
Att det betalade flottas rulls av fastan national kapital Washington D.C.

12
00:07:14,963 --> 00:07:19,968
av ett överskott, speciellt i Pennsylvania, West Virginia och Ohio, har tagit en terrific toll.

13
00:07:21,439 --> 00:07:22,740
En annan Johnstown-flod.

14
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:25,502
Vattnet som rör sig runt om i landet har glömt flera hundra.

15
00:07:25,521 --> 00:07:36,627
I Pittsburgh-området och i Wheeling, Väst-Virginia, var de här scenerna sammanfattade med den tillfälliga rörelsen av rörelser som rör sig i stjärnade städer, som förvandlar sträckorna till en mörk utsläpp av vatten.

16
00:07:36,648 --> 00:07:43,350
Titta på den trädgård i nedre framtiden, som är förstörd av den oerhörda kraften av en utsatt kraft.

17
00:07:46,088 --> 00:07:49,690
Mörkret, devastation och mörkret rullar de springflödena.

18
00:07:49,750 --> 00:07:57,437
Det värsta av en års tid i öst.

19
00:07:59,139 --> 00:08:01,081
Skurrande vatten, röda torren, röda mörkret.

20
00:08:01,100 --> 00:08:06,906
De 14 östländska staten i värsta flöden i en års tid har tagit en tål större än kriget.

21
00:08:09,855 --> 00:08:18,838
Vi finns med i Johnstown, Pennsylvania, att ha ett av de fladdring till mindre har av ett av Johnstown fladdring 1889, vilket tog 2200 lives.

22
00:08:20,759 --> 00:08:31,225
Här är det eftermatt av fladd, räckage, en slimy modd, everywhere, en nus där slipper i is, en stick i en slu, en klamme i en städ, en breeding place for disease and play.

23
00:08:35,355 --> 00:08:39,597
Downtown Pittsburgh, America's steel capital, was turned into a city of canals.

24
00:08:39,937 --> 00:08:44,120
Its famous golden triangle held fast in the grip of floodwaters.

25
00:08:44,159 --> 00:08:49,942
Paralyzed by the torrent for a time, Pittsburgh rallied, even while rescue parties saved maroon residents.

26
00:08:55,105 --> 00:08:57,985
In the railroad yards, some cars were completely submerged.

27
00:08:59,826 --> 00:09:02,388
Martial law ruled the business district to prevent looting.

28
00:09:08,347 --> 00:09:23,956
Fires like this oil blaze added to the terror of Pittsburgh's flood.

29
00:09:24,176 --> 00:09:26,778
In Wilkes-Barre, the floodwaters wrought havoc too.

30
00:09:27,097 --> 00:09:28,639
Many were driven from their homes.

31
00:09:28,678 --> 00:09:29,499
Many were marooned.

32
00:09:37,894 --> 00:09:45,298
The United States Coast Guard, manning boats which were hastily rushed into the flood area, cruised about the town to rescue isolated families.

33
00:09:45,317 --> 00:09:47,479
The American Red Cross was right on the job as usual, the first to aid disaster victims.

34
00:09:47,519 --> 00:09:49,279
Upstate New York, like the Bingham district, suffered heavy damage.

35
